app.title: Supplementary Materials
app.p: The following are available online at https://www.mdpi.com/2218-1989/9/3/40/s1, Table S1. Fatty acid (FA) composition of the brain (cortex, striatum, hippocampus and cerebellum) from weaning mice reared by dams fed control or DHA-supplemented (1%, w/ w) diets. Table S2. Fatty Acid (FA) composition of plasma and heart from weaning mice reared by dams fed control or DHA-supplemented (1%, w/ w) diets. Table S3. Experimental mouse diets. Table S4. Fatty acid composition of diets. Table S5. Method validation parameters for detection of 4-HHE in plasma, heart and brain tissue. Table S6. Method validation parameters for detection of 4-HNE in plasma, heart and brain tissue.
